Calendar pad with 3 months in a row and an ability to switch months.

Based on Mootools (http://mootools.net)

Requires:
* Mootools Core 1.2.4
* Mootools More 1.2.4:
  - Date
  - Hash.Extras
  - String.Extras
  - Element.Delegation

